### ============================================================
### ReassessmentController - API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment
### ============================================================

### [1] GET reassessment dashboard
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment
X-User-Role: NURSE

###

### [2] GET reassessment dashboard - as MANAGER
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment
X-User-Role: MANAGER

###

### [3] GET reassessment form for a care plan
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment/1
X-User-Role: NURSE

###

### [4] GET reassessment form - plan not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment/9999
X-User-Role: NURSE

###

### [5] POST submit reassessment - full payload
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: NURSE

{
  "reassessmentReason": "90-day cycle review",
  "goals": [
    {
      "description": "Improve mobility with walker assistance",
      "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
    },
    {
      "description": "Maintain skin integrity - no new pressure ulcers",
      "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
    }
  ],
  "interventions": [
    {
      "description": "Assist with ambulation twice daily",
      "assignedRole": "CNA",
      "frequency": "TWICE_DAILY"
    },
    {
      "description": "Reposition every 2 hours",
      "assignedRole": "CNA",
      "frequency": "EVERY_2_HOURS"
    }
  ]
}

###

### [6] POST submit reassessment - significant change trigger
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment/2
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: MANAGER

{
  "reassessmentReason": "Significant Change in Status (SCS) - fall incident",
  "goals": [
    {
      "description": "Prevent fall recurrence",
      "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
    }
  ],
  "interventions": [
    {
      "description": "Fall prevention protocol - bed alarm, non-slip socks",
      "assignedRole": "RN",
      "frequency": "DAILY"
    }
  ]
}

###

### [7] POST submit reassessment - minimal payload (no goals/interventions)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment/3
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: NURSE

{
  "reassessmentReason": "Routine review",
  "goals": [],
  "interventions": []
}

###

### [8] FORBIDDEN - wrong role (CNA cannot submit reassessment)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Role: CNA

{
  "reassessmentReason": "Test",
  "goals": [],
  "interventions": []
}

###

### [9] UNAUTHORIZED - no role header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/reassessment

###
